<h1 class="headline" itemprop="headline">
                        <span class="productSpan">
                                                    <span class="itemreviewed" itemprop="itemReviewed">Microsoft Surface Pro 4</span> review:
                            </span>
        
        A refined Surface Pro is still the king of the tablet PC hill

    </h1>
<div class="metaData">
    
    <span class="authors">
