    </div><p> 	 	But don't take my word for it. We were able to coax comic book writer and artist <a href="https://twitter.com/parentdaniel" target="_blank" data-component="externalLink">Dan Parent</a>, best known for his work on "Archie" comics, to test drive both the Surface Pro 4 and the Surface Book. As an illustrator who works both on paper and in programs such as Photoshop, he was impressed by the feel of the Surface Pen and especially its eraser. You can see more of his reactions and a live drawing demo in our video.</p><div class="shortcode gallery size_small" data-component='["ellipsis"]' section="shortcodeGallery">
